---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | FreeOnlyFanz"
  description="Privacy policy for FreeOnlyFanz: what we collect, cookies, and outbound links."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
  <article class="info-page container">
    <header class="info-page-header">
      <p class="info-eyebrow">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="info-page-body">
      <p>
        This page is a plain-language summary, not legal advice. If you need certainty for your situation, talk to someone
        qualified in your jurisdiction.
      </p>
      <h2>What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        Like most sites, we may receive basic technical data when you visit (for example IP address, browser type, and rough
        region). If we use analytics, those tools have their own policies.
      </p>
      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        We may use cookies or similar tech for traffic measurement or site function. You can control cookies in your browser
        settings.
      </p>
      <h2>Outbound links</h2>
      <p>
        When you follow a link to another site, that site sets its own rules. We do not control their privacy practices.
      </p>
      <h2>Affiliate and sponsored links</h2>
      <p>
        Some outbound links may be sponsored or affiliate links. If you use them, third parties may know you came from a
        referral.
      </p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy: see <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
